    "description": {
      "value": "<p>When you cast a cantrip with a casting time of an action, you can use one of your Alchemical Formula as a Bonus Action even if they would normally require a Magic action.</p><p>Additionally, you can cast @UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.spells.Item.matSplLesserRest]{Lesser Restoration} without expending a spell slot and without preparing the spell, provided you use @UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.class-and-subclass-features.Item.JT7RobJSiQVCO1dh]{Alchemist's Satchel} within reach. Your Lesser Restoration adds the &amp;Reference[Charmed apply=false], &amp;Reference[Frightened apply=false] or &amp;Reference[Weakened apply=false] condition as one condition that can end. You can do so a number of times equal to your Intelligence modifier (minimum of once), and you regain all expended uses when you finish a Long Rest.</p>",
